units real
dimension 3
boundary p p p
atom_style charge
box tilt large
processors * * *


read_data MoS2.input
replicate 10 10 10 
mass 1 95.95
mass 2 32.065

# mass 3  1.008


pair_style reaxff NULL safezone 16.0 mincap 2400
pair_coeff * * ffield.reax Mo S

fix 1 all qeq/reax 1 0.0 10.0 1.0e-6 reaxff

thermo 10
thermo_style custom step pe temp lx 

dump restart_dump all custom 100 MoS2.dumptraj id type q x y z
dump_modify restart_dump sort id

timestep  0.1
fix sample all nvt temp 300.0 300.0 10.0
run 5000
